Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:11.23,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:15.03,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:22.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:26.53,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:30.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.21,0:00:33.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.88,0:00:36.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:40.10,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:44.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.48,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.98,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.69,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:59.21,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.72,0:01:11.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:15.33,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.33,0:01:18.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,140.389)}Three Electric Monsters:
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs185\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,710.389)}the Seadragons!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.64,0:01:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Things have been too quiet\Nlately. It's boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.78,0:01:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider Kid Corps\Nhaven't had anything to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting soft!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so snotty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.48,0:01:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure something terrible\Nwill happen very soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on by!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.43,0:02:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got monsters straight\Nfrom America, fresh in a can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.35,0:02:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on by!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.87,0:02:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters in a can?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.15,0:02:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.25,0:02:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a monster in a can!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster in a can...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You think it's legit?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How much is it, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.05,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a great price.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,200 yen apiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.60,0:02:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have three, so how\Nabout you take one each?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds fun, so maybe I'll buy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sure.\N- I'll get one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.28,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Me, too!\N- Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here.\N- Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,- Here.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Put them in water and they'll grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll show me once\Nit's big and strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We will, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.25,0:03:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bring it back\Nonce it's this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It says here they don't\Nget bigger than one centimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.64,0:03:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,if you raise them very carefully,\Nthey could even get this big!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.80,0:03:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna put mine in an aquarium!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the monster gonna be born?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Two o'clock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Got done earlier than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.68,0:05:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.53,0:06:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not how you'd\Nexpect it to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing left of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a heap of scrap metal...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A normal fire wouldn't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the three workers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the real mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's as if they just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They weren't the only ones attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing happened to Choco.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It means the three who bought\Nthe monsters in a can were attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.31,0:07:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters in a can?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What's really strange is that all the aquariums\Nthe monsters were put in were broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you buy those cans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.96,0:07:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.73,0:07:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.26,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go around back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.52,0:08:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takeshi, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoki!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.52,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dirty trick...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Hongo?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.86,0:08:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream louder, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've interfered in Shocker's plans\Nof conquest time and again...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're helpless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your latest cyborg, Seadragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be functioning just as expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Electric monster Seadragon will\Nelectrocute any who resist it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.12,0:09:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,with the high-voltage electricity\Nstored in its antenna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever Seadragon goes,\Nmountains of the dead will follow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo, I am Shocker's cyborg, Seadragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take one more step, and the child dies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.11,0:09:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You damned Shocker monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.35,0:09:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one you're after, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the child go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.65,0:10:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill this child, and then you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:13.76,Bumper Episode 70-98,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\c&HE4EBE4&\pos(320,534)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, get him to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Grab them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Lost your nerve, Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,12,000 volts run through these antennae...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn you to ash\Ninstantly, just like that car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:22.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,I see... it's this electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:25.40,Italics,,0,0,0,,He must have immolated\Nthe workers along with their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.86,0:11:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider... this is your end!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.72,0:12:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,His legs are his weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider has identified\NSeadragon's weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Use the other two Seadragons\Nto destroy the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've fixed Seadragon's weak point.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider's life\Nwill soon be extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.26,0:13:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.54,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.92,0:13:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.52,0:13:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.61,0:13:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.70,0:13:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.97,0:14:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.94,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never get in my way again!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.38,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hongo disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better tell HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Seadragon II.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.40,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.66,0:15:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The electrocution has rendered Hongo\NTakeshi in a state of near-death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's finish him off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand the thought\Nof killing him so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's destroyed too many of\Nour precious cyborgs in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's foiled more Shocker\Nplans than we can count.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is our mortal enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.28,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I will make him an evil incarnate,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,from the top of his head\Nto the bottom of his toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Open a hole in the top of his skull.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.65,0:15:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll replace his cerebrum\Nand cerebellum with an evil AI.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, you will be reborn
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,as Shocker's greatest servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's odd...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:17:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only playing\Npossum to find your base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.50,0:17:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your plans won't succeed,\Nas long as I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch him, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Seadragon II... show him your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.24,0:19:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Seadragon III, show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What? \NSeadragon III is here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:49.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.91,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:56.55,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:20:00.13,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:03.73,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:07.36,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:10.85,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:14.07,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:18.08,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.08,0:20:21.54,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.45,0:20:32.24,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:35.81,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies made of demons
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.81,0:20:39.44,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:43.12,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:46.62,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:50.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my scarf of red...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:53.79,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:57.38,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:21:01.05,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:04.89,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:15.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:19.20,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,with its armies spreading fear
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.20,0:21:22.69,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten our towns,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.69,0:21:25.98,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:29.93,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:33.50,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,With my mask of green...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:37.22,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.00,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:44.37,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.37,0:21:48.25,Insert Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.89,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... I will burn you to a crisp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Rider?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.85,0:21:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.76,0:21:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous. Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.96,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.70,0:22:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.57,0:22:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I finished off all three Seadragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.35,0:22:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody safe here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All three Seadragons are gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.81,0:22:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But how did you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe that to the boys here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, how many of the\NSeadragons did you beat, Mr. Taki?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.72,0:22:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider didn't beat all three\Nhimself, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did Rider go anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.86,0:22:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He was just there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.64,0:23:01.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider beat all three\NSeadragons that Shocker was so proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.94,0:23:06.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Shocker was already\Ncreating its next terrible cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.72,Cont,,0,60,155,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.03,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,0)\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs60\fnCalibri\pos(310.175,302.203)\c&HFFFFFF&}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.04,0:23:17.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Its long red tongue snakes out creepily.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Rider's body burns in red.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Wretched Rider...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:26.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The flaming-hot tongue of\NImoriges will melt you into goo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:30.99,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Stay tuned to this channel next week for "Showdown at Hell Ranch!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,190.389)}The Monster Imoriges
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:30.99,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs145\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(477.167,700.389)}Showdown at Hell Ranch!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:50.41,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kicking off the ground with a Rider Jump,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.41,0:23:57.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,a great turbine that\Nwhirls through the air!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:01.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Calling up lightning with a Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.58,0:24:05.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Striking down enemies with a Rider Chop!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.40,0:24:09.00,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.00,0:24:13.06,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.93,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Three Electric Monsters:\Nthe Seadragons!!